What you need to know:  His sentiments were echoed by the SOYA panel of judges chairperson Chris Mbaisi who noted that a good name is key to good performance and legacy building for future generations in the sporting industry.“Our sports icons are our representatives as Kenya. What they do out there leaves indelible marks and the generations to come will follow suit. As the panel of judges, we continue to encourage our sportsmen and women to set a good example to the upcoming generations by playing clean,” said Mbaisi.